   CONTINUATION OF THE NOVEMBER 2000 MEETING TO IMPROVE THE WATER RIGHTS
   PROCESS AND PROCEDURES

   In November 2000, the SWRCB held a public workshop to receive comments
   and recommendations on actions that could be taken to improve the Water
   Rights process. Those comments and suggestions have been analyzed and
   the SWRCB will schedule an additional public meeting to receive comment
   on that analysis.

   SWRCB NOTICE OF AN ADDITIONAL PUBLIC MEETING FOR SEPT. 5, 2001

   SWRCB NOTICE OF NOVEMBER 27, 2000, PUBLIC MEETING

   ANALYSIS OF THE WATER RIGHTS PROCESS AND PROCEDURES MEETING

